Defendant must submit a DNA sample.  Defendant shall write a letter of apology to the victim due within 30 days and preapproved by agent.  Defendant shall attend counseling as deemed appropriate by agent.  Defendant shall pay supervision fees as ordered by the Department of Corrections.
